THIS FANEDIT ONLY INCLUDES THE DC BACKUP STORY PIPELINE FEATURING RENEE MONTOYA

This DIGITAL release is an updated version; this new version uses digital cbr sources so the pictures are sharper and have better contrast and color.

Do you like the DC Comics character Renee Montoya? Do you like the crime fighter The Question?

If yes, this 106 page FANEDIT of Detective Comics Pipeline should be very enjoyable. Pipeline consists of 2 chapters and spans 11 issues of Detective Comics from 854 (2009-08) to 865 (2010-07). Pipeline follows up on Renee's big adventure with The Spectre, her former partner Crispus Allen, in Final Crisis: Revelations (2007-2008). Pipeline shows Renee again traveling the world to combat slavers and finally encounter a terrible old enemy. The Huntress (Helena Bertinelli) joins up with Renee and battles along her side to the end. As is typical, Renee leaves Helena to ponder a final tantalizing Question at the end. This is the last of Renee's starring roles in the Pre-Flashpoint New Earth era - hopefully DC will bring Renee back soon.
